---
import "../style/global.css";
const siteTitle = "FAQ - Questions Theo Is Tired Of Answering";
const description =
  "Y'all ask some dumb stuff so I put answers to all of it here";
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <meta name="description" content={description} />
    <meta name="twitter:image" content="https://t3.gg/images/twitter.png" />
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
    <meta name="twitter:creator" content="@t3dotgg" />
    <meta property="og:title" content={siteTitle} />
    <meta property="og:description" content={description} />
    <meta property="og:image" content="https://t3.gg/images/twitter.png" />
    <title>{siteTitle}</title>
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#000000" />

    <script defer data-domain="astro.t3.gg" src="https://t3.gg/js/script.js"
    ></script>
  </head>

  <body class="flex justify-center w-full">
    <main
      class="relative flex flex-col items-center max-w-2xl px-4 py-8 text-black"
    >
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center w-full text-center">
        <h1 class="pt-2 text-4xl font-bold">Theo's FAQ</h1>
        <h2 class="text-2xl">Stop asking me dumb shit</h2>
        <div class="text-xl italic">
          Navigate this page by reading it or CMD+F for the thing you want to
          ask
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="py-2"></div>
      <div class="flex flex-col w-full text-xl links">
        <h4 class="pt-4 font-bold" id="flutter">Do you recommend Flutter?</h4>
        <div>No.</div>

        <h4 class="pt-4 font-bold" id="editor">What editor do you use?</h4>
        <div>VS Code.</div>

        <h4 class="pt-4 font-bold" id="theme">
          What theme do you use in VS Code?
        </h4>
        <div>Poimandres theme.</div>

        <h4 class="pt-4 font-bold" id="theme">
          What program do you use for your diagrams?
        </h4>
        <div><a href="https://excalidraw.com/">Excalidraw</a>.</div>

        <h4 class="pt-4 font-bold" id="plugins">
          What plugins do you use in your editor?
        </h4>
        <div>Nothing special.</div>

        <h4 class="pt-4 font-bold" id="improvement">
          How do I get better at programming?
        </h4>
        <div>Build shit.</div>

        <h4 class="pt-4 font-bold" id="solid">
          What are your thoughts on Solid?
        </h4>
        <div>Pretty cool.</div>

        <h4 class="pt-4 font-bold" id="angular">
          What are your thoughts on Angular?
        </h4>
        <div>Pretty bad.</div>

        <h4 class="pt-4 font-bold" id="other-frameworks">
          What are your thoughts on Vue/Svelte/Marko/Quik?
        </h4>
        <div>I don't think about them too much.</div>

        <h4 class="pt-4 font-bold" id="languages">
          What languages do you code in?
        </h4>
        <div>Typescript.</div>

        <h4 class="pt-4 font-bold" id="other-languages">
          What OTHER languages do you code in?
        </h4>
        <div>Typescript.</div>

        <h4 class="pt-4 font-bold" id="elixir">...seriously?</h4>
        <div>I wrote some Elixir back in the day.</div>

        <h4 class="pt-4 font-bold" id="typescript">
          Why do you like Typescript?
        </h4>
        <div>It's like JS but easier.</div>

        <h4 class="pt-4 font-bold" id="javascript">
          Why don't you like Javascript?
        </h4>
        <div>It's like TS but harder.</div>

        <h4 class="pt-4 font-bold" id="new-project">
          What should I use to start a new project?
        </h4>
        <div><a href="https://init.tips">init.tips</a>.</div>

        <h4 class="pt-4 font-bold" id="ping-stack">
          What stack does Ping.gg use?
        </h4>
        <div><a href="https://init.tips">init.tips</a>.</div>

        <h4 class="pt-4 font-bold" id="sure-about-flutter">
          Are you sure you don't like Flutter?
        </h4>
        <div>
          <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RNo1v8DPWk4">Yes</a>.
        </div>

        <h4 class="pt-4 font-bold" id="sure-about-flutter">
          Are you REALLY sure? I heard Flutter is faster than React Native.
        </h4>
        <div>
          <a
            href="https://thomasmiddel.medium.com/flutter-its-poor-ios-performance-84ec1eacd235"
            >Yes</a
          >. I am <a href="https://github.com/flutter/flutter/issues/76180"
            >quite certain</a
          >.
        </div>

        <div class="py-4"></div>
      </div>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
